</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Over the course of the six-month off-leash trial period for dogs in two Santa 
Monica parks, neighbors adjacent to Joslyn Park documented and reported more 
than 200 violations of the city ordinance.We also voiced concern over conflicts 
with county health and safety codes. 
</P>
