COMMUNITY NEWS: AZUSA; MEMORIAL FUND TO HELP FAMILY OF CRASH VICTIM 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The Azusa Police Department and the Los Angeles County Fire Department have 
set up a memorial fund for a 17-month-old girl who was killed when her parents' 
car was hit by a drunk driver. 
</P>
<P>
