killed on July 22. The police department and L.A. County Fire Department 
Station 32 have set up a fund at Wells Fargo Bank (700 N. Azusa Ave. in Azusa) 
to help the family. Donations can be made to the Rachel Suzanne Prado Memorial 
Fund.  
