<P>
AFTERSHOCK WATCH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 No Northridge earthquake aftershocks greater than magnitude 3.0 were recorded 
between 8 p.m. Tuesday and 8 p.m. Wednesday, according to Caltech. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
