<P>
LAS VEGAS ARMORED TRUCK DRIVER SOUGHT IN APPARENT THEFT OF $1 MILLION 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Authorities are searching for a 23-year-old armored truck driver and her 
boyfriend after the driver disappeared with $1 million in cash. The heist was 
the third involving an armored truck in Las Vegas in the past 10 months. 
</P>
<P>
 Police were searching for Misty Leann Smith, a Brinks employee since April 1, 
