<HEADLINE>
<P>
SURVIVORS SOUGHT AFTER RUSSIA DAM BURSTS; 12 DIE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Rescuers in helicopters and on land searched Tuesday for dozens of people 
washed away when a dam burst in the Ural Mountains.At least 12 people were 
confirmed killed and officials listed 70 as missing. 
</P>
<P>
 A wall of water swept over four villages when the dam on the Tirlyan reservoir 
collapsed Sunday night after heavy rains. About 750 people were evacuated from 
the Beloretsk region downriver. 
</P>
