<P>
ORANGE COUNTY FOCUS: MISSION VIEJO; ENSEMBLE CONDUCTOR SEEKS NEW MUSICIANS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By JEFF BEAN 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Jennifer McBride has been selected to conduct the symphonic wind ensemble and 
pep band at Saddleback College. 
</P>
<P>
 McBride of Laguna Beach replaces Monte C. La Bonte, a longtime faculty member 
who died last spring. 
</P>
<P>
 McBride is seeking new members for both musical groups. 
</P>
<P>
 The symphonic wind ensemble is made up local residents and high school and 
college students. Rehearsals are held from 7 to 10 p.m. Tuesdays for six 
concerts over its nine-month season. 
</P>
<P>
 The pep band plays at Saddleback College football and basketball games and 
rallies. For more information, call (714) 582-4747.JEFF BEAN 
</P>
