International Securities, who predicted the index is headed for the 800-point 
mark. 
</P>
<P>
 Zhang Lai, an International Securities analyst, said a powerful technical 
correction that dragged the index down by 13.11% on Tuesday was checked in the 
morning as investors moved in from the sidelines. 
